Even if you feel that experiment has yielded mixed results, it’s far more Interesting than letting everyone know you don’t need to fight crowds to see a da Vinci. One is the American Dream realized, the other is that same dream deferred.

You tell me he couldn’t assemble Pharrell and Dave Sitek and the, probably, 20 other musical geniuses on this track, and make world dominating pop rap r&b album.

But instead he decides to make 7 song twenty minute records, one of which is a coke rap album with Whitney Houston’s

At least Kanye is interacting with the world on some level. And, I know the whole thing here is that you closed down that museum and you are Kings and Queens again. Respect. But at least Kanye is willing to fall flat on his face in service of finding something new.

Rare moments of introspection are, too, not introspection but a sterile interpretation of what having self-awareness would look like. THIS is narcissism: nothing behind the masks, except throbbing pain of envy, paranoia, hubris and delusional pride.
